messages.message: @Liam Callanan any chance you have access to the app that caused the error for you? It probably needs to be a situation where somehow a dict_list is typed as a table in human review instead of a dict_list
Nvm, I see it happening for all dict_list types potentially

Alright so issue with the errors when editing `DICT_LIST` were due to the code trying to convert it from a `DICT_LIST` format to `TABLE` format twice and it could only be done once. Adding a check seems to have fixed it. I'll investigate a bit to see how far back we need to backport this.
Fix here: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/64684 need to backport to 24.40
